      "start": 16.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 39.619998931884766,
      "text": "I'm saying farewell to the rubble on my shoulders of responses",
      "start": 31.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 45.97999954223633,
      "text": "I'm saying farewell for thinking that I can be",
      "start": 40.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 51.599998474121094,
      "text": "Partnered up with someone eventually to see me for me",
      "start": 46.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 56.97999954223633,
      "text": "But they never do, they only see the complicated robots I set in front of them",
      "start": 51.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 64.76000213623047,
      "text": "Instead of personalizing it's just me, I'm just not the right way",
      "start": 57.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 78.72000122070312,
      "text": "So with all this under me I say farewell to these thoughts of me",
      "start": 64.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 88.04000091552734,
      "text": "I can't worry about your response to my needs",
      "start": 80.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 96.94000244140625,
      "text": "I can't compromise me to make this moment last",
      "start": 89.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 100.72000122070312,
      "text": "Cause if you want it, you want it, there's no way to say it",
      "start": 96.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 104.55999755859375,
      "text": "Certain ways are nice, if you don't you just don't",
      "start": 101.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 112.44000244140625,
      "text": "Let me move on, back to me",
      "start": 105.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 120.5999984741211,
      "text": "Cause I need someone who knows me, someone who loves me, someone who doesn't",
      "start": 112.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 125.58000183105469,
      "text": "Mad at my little bit of me I try to ask for",
      "start": 120.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 138.33999633789062,
      "text": "So I say farewell to all the things that tell me not to be there for me",
      "start": 126.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 143.44000244140625,
      "text": "And make it easier",
      "start": 138.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 152.66000366210938,
      "text": "So I'm not gonna just be silent, I'm not just gonna die in obscurity",
      "start": 144.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 159.67999267578125,
      "text": "Cause that wouldn't be fair to me",
      "start": 154.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 163.67999267578125,
      "text": "So as you say goodbye to you that you lost inside of you",
      "start": 159.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 166.8000030517578,
      "text": "And you say farewell to the thing that you thought was you",
      "start": 163.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 171,
      "text": "I hope you feel all up on your knees",
      "start": 166.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 174.72000122070312,
      "text": "The moment you know",
      "start": 171.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 180.6999969482422,
      "text": "That it never comes back",
      "start": 175.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 189.82000732421875,
      "text": "Thanks for watching!",
      "start": 188.4199981689453
    }
  ],
  "unlock": {
    "card": "card-261",
    "fragments": 10
  }
}